window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b><i>Running away is never the answer.</i></b><br> </p> <p>After escaping from the Rogue Sect, John and Sarah find something new about each other. They're both Siders. Their path of loneliness will now take a turn, finding new allies in the most unexpected of places.<br> </p> <p>But good things come hand-in-hand with the bad. <br> </p> <p>Elder Han and his son are not willing to give up their chase. Chris's obsession over possessing Sarah's body for himself is not to be taken lightly. Nor is his father's. <br> </p> <p>Fight or flight, it's now their choice.<br> </p> <p>Join John and Sarah in a new issue of The Idle System to find out what happens next!</p>"; 
